name: testRenameFromSideMenu
description: Verify that the 'Multibranch Pipeline' can be renamed from side menu on the Project page
descriptionHtml: Verify that the 'Multibranch Pipeline' can be renamed from side menu on the Project page

testStage.description: Verify that the 'Multibranch Pipeline' can be renamed from side menu on the Project page

steps.name: Click on 'New Item' in the side menu
Click 'Save' button on the BaseConfigPage page
Click 'Logo' button and move to main page
Click on the 'Rename' Button on the Base Job Page
Get the name of the job from Base Job Page
